"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1929475-helen-skelton-olympics-bbc-dress\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  BBCpresenterHelen Skeltononce suffered an awkward wardrobe malfunction as she opted for a stunning red dress to present theOlympicsin 2016.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Helen later hinted that she thought herglamorous outfits may have been the reason why she wasn't asked back to host the coveragefor the next tournament.\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, Helen was presenting on stage outside Buckingham Palace for the Olympic Parade, but struggled to keep her skirt under control due to the weather conditions.\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The beloved TV host suffered an awkward wardrobe malfunction, leaving viewers at home gobsmacked as they rushed to social media to point out the embarassing moment.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One said: \\\"Oh Helen Skelton, flashing Chris Hoy!\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Crying with laughter, all it takes is a gust of wind!\\\"\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another added: \\\"Misjudging a flowing skirt on a windy day, rookie mistake.\\\"\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Helen's daring outfits commanded attention throughout the coverage, and the star later admitted she thought her wardrobe was a part to play in her being snubbed for the next gig.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheBBCtold her that they were \\\"downsizing\\\" their coverage, and Helen graciously accepted that it was not meant to be.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said at the time: \\\"Now the story's evolved into something else.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like if I do not get a gig on sport it's because of the shorts.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did Rio and then I did the Budapest World Swimming Championships in 2017 and I have not done anything else since.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So\\u2026\\\"  Do not miss:BBC presenter Alex Scott shares career update after Olympics snub  Do not miss:BBC iPlayer dramas you can watch instead of Olympics  Do not miss:One of the best horror films ever is streaming on BBC iPlayer for limited time  When questioned further about the link between her outfits and her axe from the team, she added: \\\"I do not know.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9992275070297152, \"rank\": 0.0007495795246531448, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex's_Lemonade_Stand_Foundation\", \"score\": 0.9979701524858603, \"rank\": 0.0017810679599789183, \"text\": \"Alex Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex's_Lemonade_Stand_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex's_Lemonade_Stand_Foundation\"}, {\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9992275070297152, \"rank\": 0.0007495795246531448, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BB